	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just searching the name turned up <a href="http://kotaku.com/5158834/the-making-of-wrestle-jam-the-wrestlers-unsung-hero" class="postlink">this article</a>, and other stuff.  While typing it in, google suggested I search for "wrestle jam rom", haha.  So it must be fairly convincing.  I'd guess it's running on a PC or whatever system that programmer can work with in a short time.
<br /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">"It was as close to a genuine old-school wrestling game as I could make it in the time allowed. I even mapped an old Nintendo controller to the input system so they could play it that way."<br /></div>

		

